WEBVTT

00:08:30.550 --> 00:08:33.268
But I also don't want you
to be disillusioned.

00:08:33.292 --> 00:08:37.021
These are not large enough
to solve our climate crisis,

00:08:37.045 --> 00:08:40.878
and so what we need to do
is we need to actually think about

00:08:40.902 --> 00:08:42.379
what it could take.

00:08:42.403 --> 00:08:46.382
One thing I'll absolutely say
is positive about the carbon markets

00:08:46.406 --> 00:08:50.998
is that they allow for new
capture plants to be built,

00:08:51.022 --> 00:08:52.925
and with every capture plant built,

00:08:52.949 --> 00:08:54.401
we learn more.

00:08:54.425 --> 00:08:55.936
And when we learn more,

00:08:55.960 --> 00:08:58.684
we have an opportunity
to bring costs down.

00:08:59.914 --> 00:09:03.441
But we also need to be willing to invest